{"body": "Because class methods do not mixin in modules. If I do:\r\n\r\n``` ruby \r\nmodule A\r\nend\r\n\r\nmodule B\r\n  def self.included(base)\r\n    base.extend ClassMethods\r\n  end\r\n\r\n  module ClassMethods\r\n    def hello\r\n      puts 'hello'\r\n    end\r\n  end\r\nend\r\n\r\nA.send(:include, B)\r\n\r\nclass C\r\n  include A\r\nend\r\n\r\n# I get\r\nA.hello\r\n\r\n# Instead of\r\nC.hello # => undefined method `hello' for C:Class (NoMethodError)\r\n```\r\n", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/2773521", "created_at": "2011-11-17T08:37:27Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/3481#issuecomment-2773521", "updated_at": "2011-11-17T08:37:27Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 3481, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bogdan/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bogdan/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bogdan/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/bogdan", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bogdan/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/bogdan", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bogdan/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://2.gravatar.com/avatar/91913f6ab8085bab0f2aa43995ba8ca2?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F926d19e70f74c20f796d376aafa3c6e2.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bogdan/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bogdan/received_events", "gravatar_id": "91913f6ab8085bab0f2aa43995ba8ca2", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bogdan/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "bogdan", "type": "User", "id": 122436, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bogdan/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "523835c9bd3543c15100fc97"}, "id": 2773521, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/3481"}
